<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Cyber Threat Dashboard - Home</title>
<style>
        /* Cybersecurity Theme */
        body {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #fff;
        }
 
        /* Add futuristic fonts */
        @@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap');
 
        header {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #00ff9f;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff9f;
        }
 
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff9f;
        }
 
        /* Section styles */
        .container {
            width: 85%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
 
        .section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 2px solid #00ff9f;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #f72585;
        }
 
        h2 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #f72585;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
 
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
 
        /* News feed */
        .news-feed {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
 
        .news-item {
            background-color: #333;
            border-left: 5px solid #00ff9f;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff9f;
        }
 
        .news-item:hover {
            background-color: #222;
        }
 
        .news-item h3 {
            color: #f72585;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
 
        .news-item p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #ccc;
        }
 
        /* Button style */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #00ff9f;
            color: #0d0d0d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            text-align: center;
            margin-right: 10px;
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
        }
 
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f72585;
            color: white;
        }
 
        /* Centered button */
        .center-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
 
        /* Diagram section */
        .diagram {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 2px solid #f72585;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ff9f;
        }
 
        .diagram img {
            width: 60%;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<h1>Cyber Threat Dashboard</h1>
</header>
 
    <div class="container">
<!-- About the dashboard -->
<div class="section">
<h2>About the Dashboard</h2>
<p>Welcome to the Cyber Threat Dashboard, your comprehensive tool for monitoring real-time cybersecurity threats.
            Our dashboard provides insights into the latest vulnerabilities, potential breaches, and threat actors.
            Explore real-time data visualizations on current cyber threats, including trends and types of attacks. Stay updated and secure your digital assets with informed decision-making.</p>
</div>
 
        <!-- News feed -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Cybersecurity News</h2>
<div class="news-feed">
<!-- News item 1 -->
<div class="news-item">
<h3>Ransomware Attacks Surge in 2024</h3>
<p>Security experts report an unprecedented rise in ransomware attacks targeting global industries.
                    Learn how companies are adapting to the evolving threat landscape.</p>
</div>
<!-- News item 2 -->
<div class="news-item">
<h3>New Phishing Techniques Unveiled</h3>
<p>Researchers have identified a new, more deceptive form of phishing attack.
                    Protect your organization by staying informed about the latest phishing techniques.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
 
        <!-- TryHackMe Room Section -->
<div class="section" id="tryhackme">
<h2>TryHackMe Room: Hacking Challenges</h2>
<p>Looking to enhance your hacking skills? Explore <a href="https://tryhackme.com/room/nameofroom" target="_blank">TryHackMe’s Hacking Room</a> 
            to participate in hands-on cybersecurity challenges and learning exercises. This room offers a variety of scenarios to test your knowledge in hacking, securing systems, and analyzing threats.</p>
<p>Start your hacking journey and test your skills with the latest challenges!</p>
</div>
 
        <!-- Diagram and Dashboards Section -->
<div class="section diagram" id="dashboard">
<h2>Dashboard Diagrams</h2>
<p>Here are some examples of how our cybersecurity dashboards visualize threats and attacks.</p>
<!-- Placeholder for dashboard images -->
<img src="dashboard_diagram.png" alt="Cybersecurity Dashboard Diagram">
</div>
 
        <!-- Navigation buttons -->
<div class="center-button">
<a href="#tryhackme" class="btn">Go to TryHackMe Section</a>
<a href="#dashboard" class="btn">Go to Dashboard Section</a>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>